com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.view
Class ListTableModel

java.lang.Object
  javax.swing.table.AbstractTableModel
      com.moneydance.modules.features.importlist.view.ListTableModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, TableModel
 class ListTableModel
extends AbstractTableModel

This class provides a TableModel implementation for a given List of Files. It takes care of the formatting and caching of its table values. The first two columns represent the name of the file and the date of its last modification, the last two columns represent the action buttons to import and delete the file, respectively.

Author:
Florian J. Breunig
